{"Id":583920,"Title":"昭恩雅四章","Dynasty":"明","Author":"霍韬","Context":"于瞻者楼，奕奕岩岩。岩岩奕奕，具美伊衔。具美具瞻，普天具瞻。鸾凤毵毵，天威烜赫。生民赖生，冢臣时兴。天功时成，于亦成名。冢臣成名，婺源之浒。银潢婺辉，毓德之所。冢臣毓德，立我哲我。天子畀宠，我其宠伊。何赫赫训言，服之训言。岂曰韦编，袭之重笺。重笺训言，巍楼是跻。维是训言，皇极是基。万邦是腓，孰迩孰遥。孚皇训言，曾不崇朝。皇言则万，皇心则一。鞠哉冢臣，对天扬述。畴测天高，畴绘天文。畴酬天恩，酬恩于昭，疢忧以劳。冢臣忧劳，孰则与阶。靡旦靡昏，天宠是怀。自位中丞，至于冢卿。大政是经，大工是程。秉心忠贞，为国股肱。翼翼绳绳，不心之宁。斯酬恩之诚斯。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"10ccc313fee115c4ea625f53e7aa55e4","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7161609,"Sentence":"于瞻者楼，奕奕岩岩。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yú zhān zhě lóu ，yì yì yán yán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161610,"Sentence":"岩岩奕奕，具美伊衔。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yán yán yì yì ，jù měi yī xián ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161611,"Sentence":"具美具瞻，普天具瞻。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jù měi jù zhān ，pǔ tiān jù zhān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161612,"Sentence":"鸾凤毵毵，天威烜赫。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"luán fèng sān sān ，tiān wēi hui hè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161613,"Sentence":"生民赖生，冢臣时兴。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shēng mǐn lài shēng ，zhǒng chén shǐ xīng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161614,"Sentence":"天功时成，于亦成名。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tiān gōng shǐ chéng ，yú yì chéng mǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161615,"Sentence":"冢臣成名，婺源之浒。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhǒng chén chéng mǐng ，wù yuán zhī hǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161616,"Sentence":"银潢婺辉，毓德之所。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǐn huáng wù huī ，yù dé zhī suǒ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7161617,"Sentence":"冢臣毓德，立我哲我。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zh